records.addlTxt:
The State files an Amended Information which amends the charges to one count PTC misdemeanor theft, contrary to sections 943.20(1)(a) & 939.05  and one count misdemeanor PTC criminal trespass to dwelling, contrary to Sections 943.14& 939.05 of the Wisconsin Statutes.
NO CONTEST pleas entered to both counts in the Amended Information.  Convicted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
2) Spend thirty (30) days in the county jail, under the Huber Law, on count 1 of 15 CF 690 only, commencing on 01-10-17 by 6:00 p.m.;
3) Have no contact with Cody Piontek and Joseph Rank or their residences and have no contact with Pawn America;
4) Have no contact with the co-defendant, Justin Anderson;
5) AODA assessment and follow through;
6) Maintain absolute sobriety;
7) Pay court costs;
8) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
9) provide DNA sample;
10) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
11) Maintain fulltime employment/schooling or work search;
12) Defendant is to testify against the co-defendant completely, truthfully and accurately if necessary;
13) Pay restitution of $1,780.00 to Cody Piontek.  Restitution is ordered joint and several with Justin Anderson.
Minutes.
